  "text": "It can be shown that the average on the right-hand side (RHS) of this relation can be written as exp(−tĤ) , whereĤ is a modified Hamiltonian. In order to obtain H, we have to multiply the terms of H corresponding to particle transitions by exp(−λ) for jumps in the positive direction and by exp(λ) for jumps in the negative direction [CITATION_1] .",
